Installation instructions for FatNS
-----------------------------------

Before you start, please make sure you have the following packages installed:

* ruby1.8
* ruby1.8-dev
* libgtk2-ruby
* libgtkhtml2-ruby
* libpcap0.8
* libpcap0.8-dev

Now you must compile the pcap extensions for ruby.

cd libpcap-ruby1.8-0.6-custom/
ruby extconf.rb
make
sudo (make install|checkinstall)

Now you may run the application. Mind you, to capture, it has to be run as
root:

sudo ruby main.rb
